<item>
            <title>[LU-19646] Improve error messages in lgss_keyring</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-19646</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Improve some error messages in lgss_keyring.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Originally, they tend to be cryptic, and code debugging oriented, being meaning less for sysadmins and are to leverage.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Let&apos;s try to improve the most important ones, with a message that sysadmin could understand to look at the right place for the possible root cause.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
